evaluare_functionala_initiala:
Diagnostic:
- Contractura trapez superior drept si sternocleidomastoidian drept;
- Restrictie mobilitate cervicala probabil C4-C5 dreapta;
- Amplitudine de rotatie spre dreapta redusa fata de stanga.
Obiective terapeutice:
- Reducerea contracturii musculare;
- Eliberarea mobilitatii articulare cervicale.
